    Scope and Contents
Minutes, working papers and reports of the Advisory Committee for the Robert H. Hayes Compensation Study (1973-1974), also known as the Hayes Committee and the Hayes Compensation Advisory Committee; the committee worked on devising point rating and job descriptions for administrative and exempt civil service staff at SSU.  
  
